Package: lpm4i
Type: Package
Title: Latent position modelling for influence
Version: 1.00
Date: 2021-07-31
Authors@R: person(given = "Riccardo", family = "Rastelli", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "riccardoras@gmail.com")
Description: Models nodal attributes of a undirected network using latent positions and the observed network structure. This package is associated to the paper Tafakori et al. (2020) "Measuring systemic risk and contagion in the European financial network" <arXiv:1911.11488>.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.19), mvtnorm
